data.description: NORTHDALE POOL HOME WITH ALL NEW APPLIANCES!!! Welcome to your beautiful pool home in a highly desirable, quiet Northdale neighborhood. Just steps to the Northdale Golf & Tennis Club and within minutes of major stores, A-rated schools, and close to the airport. This large 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath, 2 car garage home on the corner lot offers a massive backyard with trees, a pool and a grilling area perfect for entertaining. The kitchen overlooks the family room. The upstairs master suite features two large walk-in closets and a dual sink. Upstairs, you will find two bedrooms with balconies separate by a full bathroom with dual sink and 4th bedroom that overlooks the pool. The roof is 10 years old, A/C unit and water heater 7. Allocation for an all-concrete Outdoor Kitchen can be included. Plans for the outdoor kitchen are included and can be included in closing. This home would be a wonderful corporate rental giving a return over 18%. Please click here for a ROI report: https://www.zilculator.com/properties/16216-Fantasia-Dr-Tampa-FL/7aa36e72 $1500 bonus with acceptance date before 11/22/2023.
